==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[ploughman]]'s [[lunch]]|pl=ploughman's lunches}}

#{{British}} A light meal of [[cheese]], [[pickled onion]]s, and a [[bread roll]]; especially one served in a [[pub]] at [[lunchtime]]. Originally devised by a marketing executive of the Dairy Council in a 1960-61 advertising campaign to sell English cheese and [[beer]].